<0xC4><0x8C>esk<0xC3><0xBD> Krumlov's Germans asked the US president in the letter not to allow "<0xC5><0xA0>umavsk<0xC3><0xA1> <0xC5><0xBE>upa" (forest region south of Bohemia) - annexed by Hitler under the Munich agreement - to be returned to Czechoslovakia.
